2.2.3 Acceptance Criteria
Phase 2 is considered complete if:
the implementation plan clearly maps the SSOT into components, services, and deployment steps
the test specification suite covers validation, normal usage, zero usage, and high usage scenarios
all formulas are directly traceable to the SSOT
the generated implementation can be verified before deployment

